arts.ttl: WCQ 2026: Senegal on the brink after South Sudan win - 2026 FIFA World Cup Qualifiers - Africa
arts.sum: Ismaila Sarr grabbed a brace to help Senegal secure a 5-0 victory over South Sudan in the 2026 FIFA World Cup qualification (Group B) match played at the Juba Stadium on Friday afternoon.
